values:
This journal is purely for role-playing purposes in the game "Where All Roads Lead"
Any resemblance to the real Matt Skiba is entirely coincidental.

Tacos accepted.

Fucking Youth Crew, assholes.
Check out this video from H20 with an itty bitty part featuring yours truly.

<lj-embed id="1"/>

I, Matt Skiba, will be leaving the fascist regime that is Chimera, and not a moment too soon. I refuse to be repressed, or stand by and watch others have their farewell notices be deleted.

And for the darlings, I'll see you in a better place for better times, where the fucking commies and the dictators are not shoving their militant rules down the throats of the innocent!

REVOLT!!!!!!


And by the way, it's "dependent". Capiche?


Love,
Matthew Thomas Skiba

So, there you have it.

Christmas is over.
2008 is here.
And according to Kanye, Jesus still walks. Or something.

Kicked it at Brandon's party with the dream-date from hell. 

Well, it wasn't really a date. 
Although we did kinda go together. 
Although he probably didn't have anyone else to go with. 
But he did ask me. 
Maybe cos everyone else had plans. 
But he could've picked anyone. 
And he picked me. 
Maybe it's cos I went with his outfit.
Yeah, thats it. 


-grin-

I'm hardcore. I can play it cool like Vanilla Ice. 

This vegan is craving some meat.

After a shitload of house-hunting, I've found a perfect little townhouse which I am very much in love with.
Right now, its a platonic love, but my feelings for the patio area (when the sun has set) is all sorts of sexual.


666 Matador Avenue.

http://community.livejournal.com/mapping_chimera/7616.html?thread=27840#t27840

Oh, hell yeah. Time to get drunk.

There comes a point in a man's life where you decide that you've just gotta get out of the fucking Hilton and find an actual apartment to live in. Seems like this might become an extended vacation.

Nothing gets me going quite like throwing empty beer cans at the television 13 year old hookers on Maury.
